verbose_text: There are conflicting experimental results regarding the manner in which a microinjection of PHB mRNA blocks cell proliferation and in the manner in wihch PHB functions as a tumor-suppressor protein and arrests G1-S cell transition through a process involving the repression of E2F mediated transcription.
evidence: tumor-suppressor protein and arrests G1-S cell transition through a process involving the repression of E2F-mediated transcription
